Program Pola Bilangan X
Kamus 
    x, i, j : integer 
Algoritma 
    Input (x)
    for i = 0 to x - 1 do 
    for j = 0 to x - 1 do
        if i = j or i + j = x - 1 then
            output(j + 1)
        else
            output(" ")
        end if
    end for
    output("\n")
    end for
end program